show.description: Once a pawn in the mafia game, she’s now back as the one pulling the strings. With every step, she rewrites the rules of the underworld. “Rebirth of a Mafia Queen” is a ruthless tale of revenge, loyalty, and a crown forged in chaos. Watch Now!
